= 1) is present on the western slope of Oriental Cordillera in Colombia (Cundinamarca) at 2240 m. a.s.l., inhabiting cloud forest in the provinces of North Andean 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Páramo">Paramo</normalizedToken>
(Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 15" captionStartId="F15" captionText="Figure 15. Biogeographical distribution of Argentinomyia andina sp. nov. (yellow), A. quimbaya sp. nov. (blue) and A. choachi sp. nov. (red)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.929.37666.figure15" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/402769" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">15</figureCitation>
